high_descs: Turn right and move towards the bedroom door then turn left and move the nightstand between the bed and the desk.
Pick up the white pencil on top of the CD on the desk.
Turn around and move to the cardboard box against the wall the turn right and move to the brown shelves on the wall.
Place the white pencil in the white mug on the shelves.
Pick up the mug containing the pencil from the shelves.
Turn around and move towards the green recycling bin then turn left and move to the desk in the corner of the room.
Place the mug containing the pencil on the desk between the CD and the edge of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug containing a pencil on the desk.

high_descs: Walk around the bed and walk towards the desk.
Pick up the white pencil from on top of the CD on the desk.
Walk across the room and face the grey shelves to your right.
Place the pencil in the white mug on the shelves.
Pick up the mug from the shelves.
Turn around and walk back to the desk.
Place the mug on the desk in front of the CD.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a pencil in it on the desk.

high_descs: Move across the room to the brown desk.
Pick up the white pencil that is on the CD.
Move across the room to the book shelf that is on the left hand side of the bed
Put the white pencil inside the white mug.
Pick up the mug with the pencil inside.
Move back across the room to the brown desk.
Place the mug with the pencil inside it on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Move mug with pencil inside to sit on the desk.

high_descs: Turn right and head towards the door, then turn left and go to the desk.  Turn right and go to the book shelf .
Pick up a pencil that is on the desk.
Turn around and move towards the open box behind you.
Put the pencil in the cup that is on the upper book shelf.
Pick up the cup with pencil in it from the shelf.
Turn to around and move towards the wall behind you.  Turn left and go to the desk ahead.
Place the cup with the pencil in it on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a pencil in a cup on the desk.

high_descs: Walk to the desk.
Pick up the white pencil on the desk.
Turn around and walk to the corner of the room with the tennis racket in it, and face the cabinets.
Place the pencil in the white mug.
Pick up the mug.
Turn around, hang left and walk back to the desk.
Put the mug on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a pencil in it on the desk.

high_descs: Turn right and walk past the bed and turn left to go stand in front of the stand to the right of the bed.
Pick up the pencil laying on top of the cd on the table to your right.
Turn around and walk until you hit the wall and then turn right and face the cabinet hanging on the wall.
Place the pencil in the white mug that's sitting on the second shelf of the cabinet on the wall.
Pick up the mug with the pencil in it.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the desk.
Place the mug near the left corner of the desk top.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a pencil in it on the desk.
